/*Base dataset of customers with early balance date (1Oct-29Feb) for 2020 period or early balance date recorded 
in income tax account attributes - priority given to period level information 
*/
	    
	    select 
	         lr2.IRD_number, lr2.Customer_key, lr2.Account_key, lr2.Account_type,  lr2.Account_Status, lr2.Acct_Close_Rsn, lr2.Ceased_date, lr2.Exemption_Rsn  
	     from 
	        (
	        select 
	                 lr1.*
	                /* to use to prioritise period level info over account level info*/
	                ,row_number() over (partition by lr1.customer_key, lr1.account_key order by lr1.record_effective_timestamp desc) as latest_record   
	        from 
	            (
                    select
                    cast(c.fstrid as int) as IRD_number,
                    b.flngcustomerkey as Customer_key, 
                    b.flngaccountkey as Account_key,
                    --a.fdtmfilingperiod as Return_Period,
                    b.fstraccounttype as Account_type, 
                    b.fstrstatus as Account_Status,
                    b.fstrclosurereason as Acct_Close_Rsn,
                    b.fdtmcease as Ceased_date,
                    d.fstrexemptionreason as Exemption_Rsn,
                    a.record_effective_timestamp  
                
                    
                FROM prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblreturn a 
                
                JOIN prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblaccount b 
                
                ON a.flngaccountkey=b.flngaccountkey
                
                
                JOIN prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblcustomerinfo c  
                
                 ON b.flngcustomerkey=c.flngcustomerkey 
                 
                left join prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblnz_accincome d
                
                on b.flngdockey = d.flngdockey
                
                 where b.flngcustomerkey < 5207808
                  
                AND a.record_active_flag = 'Y' 
                AND b.record_active_flag = 'Y' 
                and c.record_active_flag = 'Y'
                AND d.record_active_flag = 'Y'
                
                AND b.fstraccounttype in ('ITN', 'IIT') 
                --and a.fdtmfilingperiod = '2019-03-31 00:00:00'
                and a.fblninerror = 0
                
                AND b.fstrclosurereason in ('EXEMPT','IMPINC')
                AND b.fstrstatus = 'CLS'
--order by a.record_effective_timestamp desc

   ) lr1
	        -- order by 1,2,3,4,5 desc
	        ) lr2
	    where lr2.latest_record =1 /*to get latest timestamp record*/
	    order by 1 asc

select
         sk_map.dip_account_sk as dip_account_gst_sk,
         sk_map.dip_account_id,
         timeline.record_effective_timestamp,
         timeline.record_expiry_timestamp,
         CAST(timeline.record_active_flag AS CHAR(1)) as record_active_flag,
         CAST('FIRST' AS VARCHAR(10)) as account_origin,
         CAST(IFNULL(CAST(sk_map.start_account_key AS VARCHAR), 'Unknown') AS VARCHAR(10)) as account_key,
         CAST(IFNULL(LPAD(CAST(tr.ird_number AS VARCHAR(10)), 9, '0'),'Unknown') AS VARCHAR(10)) as account_ird_number,
         CAST('N/A' AS VARCHAR(30)) as start_account_id,
         CAST('N/A' AS VARCHAR(10)) as start_profile_number,
         CAST('N/A' AS VARCHAR(50)) as start_parent_profile_type,
         CAST('N/A' AS VARCHAR(10)) as start_parent_profile_number,
         CAST(IFNULL(CAST(tr.location_number AS VARCHAR), 'Unknown') AS VARCHAR(10)) as heritage_location_number,
         CAST(CASE WHEN c.cust_type = 'ORG' THEN IFNULL(legn.organisation_name, 'Unknown')
                   WHEN c.cust_type = 'IND'  THEN CONCAT(legn.title, ' ', legn.first_names, ' ', legn.surname) 
                  ELSE 'Unknown' 
         END AS VARCHAR(255)) as legal_name,
         CAST(tradn.organisation_name AS VARCHAR(255)) as trading_name,
         CAST(IFNULL(mp_tt.dip_description, IFNULL(INITCAP(tt.description), 'Unknown')) AS VARCHAR(255)) as account_type,
         CAST(IFNULL(mp_tt.dip_code_value, IFNULL(tr.tax_type, 'Unknown')) AS VARCHAR(30)) as account_type_code,
         timeline.lower_cutoff as account_start_date,
         CASE WHEN tr.treg_date_end BETWEEN '1880-01-01' and NOW()         AND
                             tr.date_ceased     BETWEEN '1880-01-01' and NOW()         AND
                             timeline.record_effective_timestamp > tr.treg_date_end    THEN tr.treg_date_end  
                   WHEN tr.treg_date_end BETWEEN '1880-01-01' and NOW()         AND
                             timeline.record_effective_timestamp > tr.treg_date_end   AND
                             tr.treg_status  = 'C'                                                              AND
                             tr.date_ceased = '9000-12-31'                                             THEN tr.treg_date_end                                              
                   ELSE  '9000-12-31' 
         END as account_ceased_date,
         CAST(CASE WHEN tr.treg_date_end BETWEEN '1880-01-01' and NOW()  AND
                             tr.date_ceased     BETWEEN '1880-01-01' and NOW()         AND
                             timeline.record_effective_timestamp > tr.treg_date_end    THEN 'Closed'
                   WHEN tr.treg_date_end BETWEEN '1880-01-01' and NOW()         AND
                             timeline.record_effective_timestamp > tr.treg_date_end    AND
                             tr.treg_status  = 'C'                                                              AND
                             tr.date_ceased = '9000-12-31'                             THEN 'Closed'                                            
                   ELSE  'Active' 
                   END AS VARCHAR(30)) as account_status,
         CAST(CASE WHEN tr.treg_date_end BETWEEN '1880-01-01' and NOW()  AND
                             tr.date_ceased     BETWEEN '1880-01-01' and NOW()         AND
                             timeline.record_effective_timestamp > tr.treg_date_end  THEN 'CLS'
                   WHEN tr.treg_date_end BETWEEN '1880-01-01' and NOW()                AND
                             timeline.record_effective_timestamp > tr.treg_date_end    AND
                             tr.treg_status  = 'C'                                     AND
                             tr.date_ceased = '9000-12-31'                             THEN 'CLS'                                            
                   ELSE  'ACT' 
                   END AS VARCHAR(10)) as account_status_code,
         CAST('TBC' AS  VARCHAR(255)) as security_level,
         CAST('TBC' AS  VARCHAR(10)) as security_level_code,
         CAST(CASE WHEN tr.treg_status = 'C' THEN IFNULL(mp_cr.dip_description, IFNULL(mp_cr2.dip_description, IFNULL(cr.description, 'Unknown')))
                                      ELSE 'N/A' 
                            END
                  AS VARCHAR(30)) as cessation_reason,
         CAST(CASE WHEN tr.treg_status = 'C' THEN IFNULL(mp_cr.dip_code_value, IFNULL(mp_cr2.dip_code_value, IFNULL(tr.cessation_reason_code, 'Unknown')))
                                      ELSE 'N/A'
                            END
         AS VARCHAR(10)) as cessation_reason_code,
         CAST(IFNULL(INITCAP(mp_ff.dip_description), IFNULL(INITCAP(ff.description), 'Unknown')) 
         AS VARCHAR(30)) as filing_frequency,
         CAST(IFNULL(mp_ff.dip_code_value, IFNULL(tr.filing_frequency, 'Unknown')) 
         AS VARCHAR(30)) as filing_frequency_code,
         CAST(IFNULL(mp_er.dip_description, IFNULL(er.description, 'Unknown')) 
         AS VARCHAR(30)) as exemption_reason,
         CAST(IFNULL(mp_er.dip_code_value, IFNULL(tr.exemption_reason_code, 'Unknown')) 
         AS VARCHAR(30)) as exemption_reason_code,
         CAST(IF(tr.exemption_reason_code IS NOT NULL, 'Y', 'N') AS CHAR(1)) as exempted_flag,
         CAST('N' AS CHAR(1)) as green_listed_flag,
         CAST('N' AS CHAR(1)) as red_listed_flag,
         CAST(IF(ah.halt_status_indicator IS NOT NULL, 'Y', 'N') AS CHAR(1)) as account_halt_flag,
         CAST(IFNULL(ac.case_open_reason_desc, 'Unknown') AS VARCHAR(30)) as audit_case_active_desc,
         CAST('Unknown' AS VARCHAR(30)) as audit_case_active_code,
         CAST(IF(ac.derived_tax_type IS NOT NULL, 'Y', 'N') AS CHAR(1)) as audit_case_active_flag,
         CAST('Unknown' AS VARCHAR(30)) as stop_mail_desc,
         CAST('Unknown' AS VARCHAR(10)) as stop_mail_code,
         CAST('N' AS CHAR(1)) as stop_mail_flag,
         CAST(IFNULL(mp_ab.dip_description, 'Unknown') AS VARCHAR(10)) as accounting_basis,
         CAST(IF(gst.nat_of_rgn = 'S', 'Special', IFNULL(mp_nor.dip_description, 'Unknown')) AS VARCHAR(10)) as registration_circumstance,
         CAST('N' AS CHAR(1)) as included_in_prices_flag,
         CAST(IF(gst.exempt_supp_ind = 'Y', 'Y', 'N') AS CHAR(1)) as exempt_supplies_flag,
         CAST(IF(gst.exp_ind IN ('E', 'B'), 'Y', 'N') AS CHAR(1)) as exporter_flag,
         CAST(IF(gst.exp_ind IN ('I', 'B'), 'Y', 'N') AS CHAR(1)) as importer_flag,
         CAST('N' AS CHAR(1)) as unpoliced_filer_flag,
         CAST(IF(gst.self_inv_ind ='Y', 'Y', 'N') AS CHAR(1)) as self_invoicer_flag,
         CAST('N' AS CHAR(1)) as hospice_filer_flag,
         CAST('N/A' AS VARCHAR(10)) as hospice_type,
         CAST('N/A' AS VARCHAR(30)) as hospice_type_desc,
         CAST('N' AS CHAR(1)) as gst_on_remote_srvcs_flag,
         CAST('N/A' AS VARCHAR(30)) as gst_on_remote_srvcs_type,
         CAST('N/A' AS VARCHAR(30)) as gst_on_remote_srvcs_code,
         CAST('N' AS CHAR(1)) as gst_zero_rated_fin_srv_flag,
         CAST('N' AS CHAR(1)) as gst_non_resident_claimant_flag,
         CAST('N' AS CHAR(1)) as taxable_activity_flag,
         timeline.insert_object_run_key,
         timeline.update_object_run_key
      from
         /* mp_cr2  */ 
         /* mp_nor  */ 
         /* mp_ab  */ 
         /* gst  */ 
         /* ac  */ 
         /* ah  */ 
         /* er  */ 
         /* mp_er  */ 
         /* ff  */ 
         /* mp_ff  */ 
         /* cr  */ 
         /* mp_cr  */ 
         /* trsc  */ 
         /* tt  */ 
         /* mp_tt  */ 
         /* c  */ 
         /* tradn  */ 
         /* legn  */ 
         /* tr  */ 
         /* sk_map  */ 
         rfn_ae_timeline_f as timeline left join 
         rfn_account_sk_map as sk_map
            on
            (
               timeline.ird_no                                       = sk_map.ird_no
               AND timeline.edw_tax_type                    = sk_map.edw_tax_type
               AND timeline.edw_location_number         = sk_map.edw_location_number
               AND timeline.record_effective_timestamp = sk_map.record_effective_timestamp
               
            ) left join 
         crw_ae_tax_registrations_wide as tr
            on
            (
               timeline.ird_no                               = tr.ird_number
               AND timeline.edw_location_number = tr.location_number
               AND timeline.edw_tax_type            = tr.tax_type
               AND timeline.record_effective_timestamp BETWEEN tr.record_effective_timestamp AND tr.record_expiry_timestamp
             --  AND timeline.record_effective_timestamp                       >= tr.treg_date_start
               AND tr.tax_type = 'GST'
               
            ) left join 
         crw_pe_client_names as legn
            on
            (
               timeline.ird_no                    = legn.ird_number
               AND legn.client_name_type = 'P'
               AND legn.location_number   = 0
               AND timeline.record_effective_timestamp BETWEEN  legn.record_effective_timestamp AND legn.record_expiry_timestamp
               
            ) left join 
         crw_pe_client_names as tradn
            on
            (
               timeline.ird_no                      = tradn.ird_number
               AND tradn.client_name_type = 'T'
               AND tradn.location_number   = 1
               AND timeline.record_effective_timestamp BETWEEN  tradn.record_effective_timestamp AND tradn.record_expiry_timestamp
            ) left join 
         crw_ae_clients as c
            on
            (
               timeline.ird_no = c.ird_number
               AND timeline.record_effective_timestamp BETWEEN c.record_effective_timestamp AND c.record_expiry_timestamp
            ) left join 
         mp_source_code as mp_tt
           ...

create table exclusion_struck_off as 
     SELECT a.ird_number,
            b.flngcustomerkey as customer_key,
            'informed via CO dataset' as struck_off_flag
            
     FROM lab_r3_assurance_project.struck_off_companies      A /* THIS TABLE IS UPDATED MONTHLY BY TOM HOLLMAN */
     INNER JOIN prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblcustomerinfo b ON cast(a.ird_number as int)  =  cast(B.fstrid as int) and fstridtype = 'IRD' 
     
     LEFT JOIN prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblindicator i ON B.flngcustomerkey = I.flngcustomerkey AND
                                      I.fstrindicator = 'INSCLF' AND
                                      I.flngver = 0 AND
                                      I.record_active_flag = 'Y' AND
                                      I.fblnactive = 1 AND
                                      (I.fdtmcease = '9999-12-31 00:00:00' OR I.fdtmcease > now()) and
                                       I.fdtmcommence IS NOT NULL
                                      
    
     WHERE B.record_active_flag = 'Y' AND
           (B.fdtmcease = '9999-12-31 00:00:00' or b.fdtmcease is null) AND
           I.flngcustomerkey  is null
           
     
     union all
     
     select distinct flngcustomerkey as customer_key,
                     ird_number,
                     'START strike off indicator'
     from prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblindicator i
     inner join 
     (
        select distinct flngCustomerKey as customer_key,
			   cast(fstrID as int) as IRD_Number
		from prod_raw_restricted_access.APP_TBLCUSTOMERINFO
		where record_active_flag = 'Y'
     ) b ON i.flngcustomerkey = b.customer_key
     where fstrindicator = 'STROFF'
       and flngver = 0
       and record_active_flag = 'Y'
       and fblnactive = 1
       and (I.fdtmcease = '9999-12-31 00:00:00' OR I.fdtmcease > now()) 
       and I.fdtmcommence IS NOT NULL

CREATE TABLE lab_r3_assurance_project.tmp_employees stored AS parquet AS
  SELECT --distinct
 Employees.fstrirdnumber AS EMPLOYEE_IRD_NUMBER , customer.fstrlistformatname as EMPLOYEE_NAME
 --, customer.fstrlistformataddress as EMPLOYEE_ADDRESS
 --, from_timestamp(employer.party_start_date, 'dd/MM/yyyy') as Emplyee_DOB
 ,
 customer.fstrzip AS EMPLOYEE_POST_CODE,
 employer.ird_number AS EMPLOYER_IRD_NUMBER --, customer.fstrtitle as EMPLOYEE_TITLE
 --, concat(nvl(customer.fstrfirstname, ''), ' ', nvl(customer.fstrmiddlename, '')) as employee_first_names
 --, customer.fstrfamilyname as EMPLOYEE_SURNAME
 ,
 CASE
     WHEN sum(employees.fcurgross) > 0 THEN 'Y'
     ELSE 'N'
 END AS Employee_paid --, case when countemp.employee_multiple_employers > 1 then 'Y' else 'N' end as employee_multiple_employers

  FROM prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblnz_rtnpsoemployeeinfo Employees
  INNER JOIN prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblreturn RETURN ON Employees.flngreturnkey = Return.flngreturnkey
  AND Return.record_active_flag = 'Y'
  AND Return.fstrreason IS NULL /*this field will be populated for removed/duplicate returns*/
  INNER JOIN lab_r3_assurance_project.tmp_latest_return latest ON Return.flngaccountkey = latest.flngaccountkey
  AND return.fdtmfilingperiod = latest.fdtmfilingperiod
  INNER JOIN prod_raw_restricted_access.app_tblcustomerinfo customer ON employees.fstrirdnumber = customer.fstrid
  AND customer.record_active_flag = 'Y'
  AND customer.flngcustomerkey != 0
  INNER JOIN prod_refined_restricted_access.party_dim employer ON latest.flngcustomerkey = cast(employer.customer_key AS int)
  AND employer.record_active_flag = 'Y'
  INNER JOIN
    (SELECT COUNT (fstrirdnumber) AS employee_multiple_employers,
                  fstrirdnumber
     FROM
       (SELECT DISTINCT fstrirdnumber,
                        flngaccountkey,
                        fdtmfilingperiod
        FROM lab_r3_assurance_project.tmp_latest_period_emp) a
     GROUP BY fstrirdnumber) countemp ON customer.fstrid = countemp.fstrirdnumber
  LEFT JOIN prod_refined_restricted_access.organisation_dim charities ON employer.customer_key = charities.customer_key
  AND charities.record_active_flag = 'Y' --and (charities.charity_org_flag = 'Y'

  AND charities.party_subtype IN ('Government Department',
                                  'Public Authority (Govt)') WHERE Return.fdtmfilingperiod >= '2020-01-01 00:00:00'
  AND charities.customer_key IS NULL
GROUP BY --customer.flngcustomerkey
 Employees.fstrirdnumber  , customer.fstrlistformatname
 -- , customer.fstrlistformataddress
 -- , customer.fstrtitle
 ,
 EMPLOYER_IRD_NUMBER,
 EMPLOYEE_POST_CODE
